freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Continue to have ms-possibly-related trigeminal nerve problem. Taking gabapentin 6x a day plus 50mg of carbamazepine at meals so I can eat. Needed to control pain. Plus I had mri for brain and spinal cord.
I had an episode with my trigeminal nerve. Last one was 5 years ago.
Relapse of MS, problem with trigeminal nerve. Having an MRI on March 15.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I took an Advil about an hour before my first Pfizer shot. I saw in the news today that the CDC is now saying that can make the immune reaction less. I have had no side effects so Im worried about the vaccine effectiveness for me.
